</center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=boum>Boum</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(3/16/02 5:40:37 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=685.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Crazy Ideas</span><hr size=1> Whatever the range, single target nukes will not make us better solo (except maybe if they go over 10 dmg/mana ratio). So these spells don't require a short range <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
